{"id":815,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":815,"title":"Jeremiah 46","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 46"],[".studySummary",["i","Jeremiah prophesies the conquest of Egypt by Babylon—Jacob will be saved and will return to his own land."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.1","order":"02.25.046.53872"},["b","1"],"The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"which came to Jeremiah the prophet against the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Gentiles"],";"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.2","order":"02.25.046.53873"},["b","2"],"Against Egypt, against the army of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Pharaoh-necho"],"king of Egypt, which was by the river Euphrates in Carchemish, which Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon smote in the fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah king of Judah."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.3","order":"02.25.046.53874"},["b","3"],"Order ye the buckler and shield, and draw near to battle."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.4","order":"02.25.046.53875"},["b","4"],"Harness the horses; and get up, ye horsemen, and stand forth with",["i","your"],"helmets; furbish the spears,",["i","and"],"put on the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"brigandines"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.5","order":"02.25.046.53876"},["b","5"],"Wherefore have I seen them dismayed",["i","and"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"turned away back"],"? and their mighty ones are beaten down, and are fled apace, and look not back:",["i","for"],"fear",["i","was"],"round about, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.6","order":"02.25.046.53877"},["b","6"],"Let not the swift flee away, nor the mighty man escape; they shall stumble, and fall toward the north by the river Euphrates."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.7","order":"02.25.046.53878"},["b","7"],"Who",["i","is"],"this",["i","that"],"cometh up as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"flood"],", whose waters are moved as the rivers?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.8","order":"02.25.046.53879"},["b","8"],"Egypt riseth up like",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"a flood"],", and",["i","his"],"waters are moved like the rivers; and he saith, I will go up,",["i","and"],"will cover the earth; I will destroy the city and the inhabitants thereof."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.9","order":"02.25.046.53880"},["b","9"],"Come up, ye horses; and rage, ye chariots; and let the mighty men come forth; the Ethiopians and the Libyans, that handle the shield; and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Lydians"],", that handle",["i","and"],"bend the bow."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.10","order":"02.25.046.53881"},["b","10"],"For this",["i","is"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"day"],"of the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts, a day of vengeance, that he may avenge him of his adversaries: and the sword shall devour, and it shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"satiate"],"and made drunk with their blood: for the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts hath a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sacrifice"],"in the north country by the river Euphrates."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.11","order":"02.25.046.53882"},["b","11"],"Go up into Gilead, and take",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"balm"],", O virgin, the daughter of Egypt: in vain shalt thou use many medicines;",["i","for"],"thou shalt not be cured."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.12","order":"02.25.046.53883"},["b","12"],"The nations have heard of thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"shame"],", and thy cry hath filled the land: for the mighty man hath stumbled against the mighty,",["i","and"],"they are fallen both together."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.13","order":"02.25.046.53884"},["b","13"],"¶The word that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake to Jeremiah the prophet, how Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon should come",["i","and"],"smite the land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Egypt"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.14","order":"02.25.046.53885"},["b","14"],"Declare ye in Egypt, and publish in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Migdol"],", and publish in Noph and in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Tahpanhes"],": say ye, Stand fast, and prepare thee; for the sword shall devour round about thee."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.15","order":"02.25.046.53886"},["b","15"],"Why are thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"valiant"],["i","men"],"swept away? they stood not, because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"did drive them."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.16","order":"02.25.046.53887"},["b","16"],"He made many to fall, yea, one fell upon another: and they said, Arise, and let us go again to our own people, and to the land of our nativity, from the oppressing sword."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.17","order":"02.25.046.53888"},["b","17"],"They did cry there, Pharaoh king of Egypt",["i","is but"],"a noise; he hath passed the time appointed."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.18","order":"02.25.046.53889"},["b","18"],["i","As"],"I live, saith the King, whose name",["i","is"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, Surely as Tabor",["i","is"],"among the mountains, and as Carmel by the sea,",["i","so"],"shall he come."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.19","order":"02.25.046.53890"},["b","19"],"O thou daughter dwelling in Egypt, furnish thyself to go into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"captivity"],": for Noph shall be waste and desolate without an inhabitant."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.20","order":"02.25.046.53891"},["b","20"],"Egypt",["i","is like"],"a very fair heifer,",["i","but"],"destruction cometh; it cometh out of the north."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.21","order":"02.25.046.53892"},["b","21"],"Also her hired men",["i","are"],"in the midst of her like fatted bullocks; for they also are turned back,",["i","and"],"are fled away together: they did not stand, because the day of their calamity was come upon them,",["i","and"],"the time of their visitation."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.22","order":"02.25.046.53893"},["b","22"],"The voice thereof shall go like a serpent; for they shall march with an army, and come against her with axes, as hewers of wood."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.23","order":"02.25.046.53894"},["b","23"],"They shall cut down her forest, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", though it cannot be searched; because they are more than the grasshoppers, and",["i","are"],"innumerable."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.24","order":"02.25.046.53895"},["b","24"],"The daughter of Egypt shall be confounded; she shall be delivered into the hand of the people of the north."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25","order":"02.25.046.53896"},["b","25"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts"],", the God of Israel, saith; Behold, I will punish",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"the"],"multitude of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"No"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_25d"},"Pharaoh"],", and Egypt, with their",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_25e"},"gods"],", and their kings; even Pharaoh, and",["i","all"],"them that trust in him:"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.26","order":"02.25.046.53897"},["b","26"],"And I will deliver them into the hand of those that seek their lives, and into the hand of Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon, and into the hand of his servants: and afterward it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"inhabited"],", as in the days of old, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.27","order":"02.25.046.53898"},["b","27"],"¶But fear not thou, O my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"Jacob"],", and be not dismayed, O Israel: for, behold, I will save thee from afar off, and thy seed from the land of their captivity; and Jacob shall return, and be in rest and at ease, and none shall make",["i","him"],"afraid."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.28","order":"02.25.046.53899"},["b","28"],"Fear thou not, O Jacob my servant, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": for I",["i","am"],"with thee; for I will make a full end of all the nations whither I have driven thee: but I will not make a full end of thee, but correct thee in measure; yet will I not leave thee wholly unpunished."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.1a","order":"02.25.046.53900"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.5"},"Jer. 1:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.15.15-29"},"25:15 (15–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.2a","order":"02.25.046.53902"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.29"},"2 Kgs. 23:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.4a","order":"02.25.046.53904"},["b","4a"],["span.small","OR"],"armor."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.5a","order":"02.25.046.53906"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"retreating."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.7a","order":"02.25.046.53908"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.7.7-8"},"Isa. 8:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/47.2"},"Jer. 47:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.22"},"Dan. 11:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.8a","order":"02.25.046.53910"},["b","8a"],["span.small","HEB"],"the river."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.9a","order":"02.25.046.53912"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19"},"Isa. 66:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/27.10"},"Ezek. 27:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/30.5"},"30:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.10a","order":"02.25.046.53914"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.15"},"Joel 1:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.10b","order":"02.25.046.53916"},["b","10b"],["span.small","OR"],"sated."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.10c","order":"02.25.046.53918"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.6"},"Isa. 34:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.11a","order":"02.25.046.53920"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/8.22"},"Jer. 8:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.8"},"51:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.12a","order":"02.25.046.53922"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.13a","order":"02.25.046.53924"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1.1-22"},"Isa. 19:1 (1–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.14a","order":"02.25.046.53926"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.1"},"Jer. 44:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.14b","order":"02.25.046.53928"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/43.7"},"Jer. 43:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.15a","order":"02.25.046.53930"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.13"},"Mosiah 1:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.24.24,26"},"Hel. 4:24 (24, 26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.19a","order":"02.25.046.53932"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/29.12"},"Ezek. 29:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/30.23.23,26"},"30:23 (23, 26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25a","order":"02.25.046.53934"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.33"},"D&C 1:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25b","order":"02.25.046.53936"},["b","25b"],["span.small","HEB"],"Amon of Thebes."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25c","order":"02.25.046.53938"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/30.14"},"Ezek. 30:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/3.8"},"Nahum 3:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"25d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25d","order":"02.25.046.53940"},["b","25d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.19"},"Jer. 25:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.30"},"44:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"25e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.25e","order":"02.25.046.53942"},["b","25e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/43.12"},"Jer. 43:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.26a","order":"02.25.046.53944"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/29.13"},"Ezek. 29:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.27a","order":"02.25.046.53946"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.13.11-13"},"3 Ne. 20:13 (11–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/22.7.6-17"},"22:7 (6–17)"],"."]]}
